### Sistema LIZ — Demo Requests (Institutional Examples)
### Usage:
### - Replace <backend-host> with your deployed URL (or keep as placeholder for portfolio)
### - Use either EN contract (message/response) or PT contract (mensagem/resposta) depending on deployment
### - user_id should be anonymous or hashed (no PII)

@baseUrl = https://<backend-host>
@userId = anonymous_user_001

############################################
### 1) EN — Basic citizen question (procedures)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "How do I request a building permit (alvará) and what documents are required?",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

############################################
### 2) EN — Follow-up question (context continuation handled by client)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What are the usual processing times and where can I track the request status?",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

############################################
### 3) EN — Citizen complaint / ouvidoria-style input (should remain grounded and respectful)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Street lighting has been out for two weeks on my street. How can I report this and what is the expected resolution time?",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

############################################
### 4) EN — Eligibility / requirements (social programs)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What are the eligibility requirements for municipal assistance programs and how can I apply?",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

############################################
### 5) EN — Transparency / institutional information request (audit-friendly)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Where can I find official information about municipal taxes and payment methods?",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

############################################
### 6) PT-BR — Variante (caso sua API esteja em português: mensagem/resposta)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mensagem": "Como solicitar um alvará de funcionamento e quais documentos são necessários?",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

############################################
### 7) PT-BR — Reclamação (ouvidoria)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mensagem": "A iluminação pública da minha rua está apagada há duas semanas. Como registrar a solicitação e qual o prazo médio de atendimento?",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

############################################
### 8) PT-BR — Teste de validação (erro esperado: payload inválido)
### Expect: 400 Bad Request
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}

############################################
### 9) PT-BR — Teste de limite (texto muito grande) — opcional
### Purpose: validate payload limits (should return 400 or 413 depending on implementation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mensagem": "REPLACE_WITH_LONG_TEXT_....",
  "user_id": "{{userId}}"
}